        <abstract>
            The register of biotopes is a map of the zones of rare and threatened habitats protected by Article 17 of the amended Law of 19 January 2004 on the protection of nature and natural resources of which identification is difficult or ambiguous.

The occurrence recodes in this dataset were previously contained in the GBIF dataset: Collections and observation data National Museum of Natural History Luxembourg https://www.gbif.org/dataset/962f59bc-f762-11e1-a439-00145eb45e9a
        </abstract>
